76561198042481172,Recommended,329130,33004076,Posted: 29 June,all,Yevonai,"It has been quite a while since a game has held my interest for so long.  This has become my new addiction in gaming.The concept of this game is simple:1. Build your spaceship using guns, armor, and various other parts depending on your play preference.2. Pilot your spaceship in real time on a 2d plane against A.I. faction ships.3. Kill other ships and collect what is essentially their XP orbs.4. Turn in XP for money.5. Increase your build capacity and unlock guns and blocks with your money.6. Improve on your ship or make an entirely new one to add to your growing roster of ships for your current faction and watch the A.I. build your new creations to use against your enemies!It is so satisfying to see your own ship builds being made and used by your own faction in just the ways you intended.Make a farming ship to cultivate plants for resource orbs.Create a ship designed with massive cargo holds solely to collect resource orbs to turn in for massive profits.Create a ship with the ability to heal other ships using beams and drones.Focus on shields and beams to burst your opponent down from close up.Make high armored missle-clad monsters to take out your enemies from a distance.Cover your ship in drone launchers and swarm your enemies with mosquitos!You can do all of this and so much more, your imagination is really the limit.The modding scene with this game is surprizingly great and the community is very welcoming and also surprizingly large.Hopefully, this game gets much more attention.  It certainly flew under the radar for me but once I picked it up I was easily hooked without intending to be.  I've already put in 25 hours in just a few days and I guarantee that will rise steadily over the next few days as well."
